buf = CircularBuffer(10)
buf.write(b'12345')
assert buf[0] == b'1'
try:
    buf[6]
except Exception as e:
    assert isinstance(e, IndexError)
assert len(buf) == 5
buf[3] = b'1'
assert str(buf) == '12315'
assert b'15' in buf
assert buf[1:1] == b''
assert buf[1:2] == b'2'
assert buf[1:] == b'2315'
assert buf[:1] == b'1'
assert buf[:-1] == b'1231'
assert buf[2:-1] == b'31'
assert buf[2:-1:2] == b'3'
assert buf[5:1:-2] == b'53'
